    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="witness" subtype="poem" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" rhyme="aa">
                <head type="title"><hi rend="caps">CASSEL</hi>.</head>
                <lg type="stanza" n="1">
                    <l>T<hi rend="smallcaps">HE</hi> way was long, and yet &#x02BC;twas sweet,&#x2014;</l> 
                    <l>Through many a shady, soft retreat,</l> 
                    <l>Where the broad willow semblance gave</l> 
                    <l>Of weeping beauty to the wave;</l> 
                    <l>And elm, with massy foliage prest,<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">5</add></l> 
                    <l>And feathery aspen&#x02BC;s quivering crest;</l>
                    <pb/><l>And many a spiry poplar glade,</l> 
                    <l>And hazel&#x02BC;s rich entangled shade;</l>                 
                    <l>While, onward as advancing still</l>                     
                    <l>From <placeName corresp="#STOMER">Omer</placeName>&#x02BC;s plain<ref type="gloss_contextual" target="cassel_glosses_contextual.php#STOMERSPLAINGLOSS"/> to <placeName corresp="#CASSEL">Cassel</placeName>&#x02BC;s hill,<ref type="gloss_contextual" target="cassel_glosses_contextual.php#CASSELLSHILLGLOSS"/><add rend="linenumber-right-JR">10</add></l>                     
                    <l>Far&#x2014;yet more far the landscape threw</l>                     
                    <l>Its deep, immeasurable blue.</l>                     
                    <l>Oh, beautiful those plains were showing,</l>                     
                    <l>Where summer sun was hotly glowing!</l>                     
                    <l>Many a battlefield lay spread&#x2014;<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">15</add></l>                     
                    <l>Once the dark dwelling of the dead:</l>                     
                    <l>But fruitful now their champaigns wave</l>                     
                    <l>With bending grain on soldier&#x02BC;s grave.</l>                     
                    <l>While far beneath in long array</l>                     
                    <l>The priestly orders wound their way;<ref type="gloss_contextual" target="cassel_glosses_contextual.php#PRIESTLYORDERSGLOSS"/><add rend="linenumber-right-JR">20</add></l>                     
                    <l>Heavy the massive banners rolled,</l>                     
                    <l>Rich wrought with gems, and stiff with gold:</l>                    
                    <l>While, as the cross came borne on high</l>                     
                    <l>Beneath its crimson canopy,</l>                     
                    <l>Many the haughty head that bowed,&#x2014;<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">25</add></l>                     
                    <l>Sunk his high crest the warrior proud,</l>                     
                    <l>The priest his glance benignant cast,</l>                     
                    <l>And murmured blessings as he past;</l>                     
                    <l>While, round the hillside echoing free,</l>                     
                    <l>Rung the loud&#x2010;hymning melody.<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">30</add></l>                     
                    <l>Many a monkish voice was there,&#x2014;</l>                     
                    <l>Many a trumpet rent the air,&#x2014;</l>                     
                    <l>And softer, sweeter, yet the same,</l>                     
                    <l>The sounds in failing cadence came.<ref type="gloss_contextual" target="cassel_glosses_contextual.php#NOMARVEL"/></l>
                    </lg>
            </div>
